Package: srorcapop
Type: Package
Title: Explores long term population trends of Southern Resident killer whales
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Maria Eleni", "Vogiatzi",
      email = "marialena26@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides a shiny app to visualize population trends of Southern 
  Resident killer whales (Orcinus orca), including census counts of 3 pods 
  (J,K,L), births and mortalities data, given by the Center for Whale Research 
  (CWR) and NOAA stock assessment reports. This package allows interactive 
  visualization of population changes over 50 years (1975-2024).
